b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2914,"category_name":"Updates","pr_category_id":"2","title_name":"Regarding Balance Adjustments to the Kaleidoscape","message":"<div>The following balance adjustments have been made to the Kaleidoscape in an update on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1646373600\\"><\/span> to make the mode more accessible and enjoyable.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Adventurers<\/div><div>\\u30fbWhen skipping to floor 30, your adventurer&#39;s starting level will be increased. (This change will not apply when skipping to floors other than 30.)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Fafnir Abilities<\/div><div>The percentage gain from upgrading these abilities beyond level 10 will be increased.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The following abilities will increase by 1.5% instead of 0.5% each level:<\/div><div>\\u30fbHP Boost<\/div><div>\\u30fbStrength Boost<\/div><div>\\u30fbSkill Damage Boost<\/div><div>\\u30fbThaumian Res, Physian Res, Demihuman Res, Therion Res, Undead Res, Demon Res, Dragon Res<\/div><div>\\u30fbDawn Amber Intake Boost<\/div><div>\\u30fbEXP Boost<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The following abilities will increase by 1% instead of 0.5% each level:<\/div><div>\\u30fbCritical Rate Boost<\/div><div>\\u30fbCritical Damage Boost<\/div><div>\\u30fbForce Strike Boost<\/div><div>\\u30fbRecovery Boost<\/div><div>\\u30fbDusk Amber Intake Boost<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Enemies<\/div><div>\\u30fbCertain enemies will have their level reduced.<\/div><div>\\u30fbCertain enemies will have their HP reduced.<\/div><div>\\u30fbMany enemies will have their strength reduced.<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe interval between the enemy&#39;s healing skills will be increased.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Bosses<\/div><div>\\u30fbAll bosses will have their HP reduced.<\/div><div>\\u30fbAll bosses will have their strength reduced.<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe interval between Harle&#39;s attacks will be increased.<\/div><div>\\u30fbHarle&#39;s attack Raven&#39;s Gale will take longer to activate.<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe Freezing Ice attacks used by the Pincers family of bosses will pursue the player for less time.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>If these adjustments are made while you are playing the Kaleidoscape, they will not be applied to your run until you suspend and resume your progress (excluding updated enemy levels, which will be applied when you advance to the next floor).<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1646373600,"prev_article_id":"2865","next_article_id":"3037","image_path":"","update_time":1646374302}}}'